subsection.def:
Administration
                    (主管機關) means the government of the state of
                whose flag the ship is entitled to fly;

tanker
                    (液貨船) means a cargo ship constructed or
                adapted for the carriage in bulk of liquid cargoes of a flammable nature;

paragraph.content:
ships to which these regulations apply or, where appropriate, the
                    particular Part or other provision in which the reference is made applies;
                    and

subparagraph.content:
3.1 bar (0.31
                        newton
                        per square millimetre);

